very deliberately is that

00:02:58.620 --> 00:03:03.500
what they imagine as great demographic
change is being done to them.

00:03:03.500 --> 00:03:08.500
And this borrows completely from the way
white nationalists also frame the issue

00:03:08.620 --> 00:03:11.820
of immigration, the issue of
demographic change in their societies.

00:03:12.100 --> 00:03:15.100
It's not surprising that
somebody like David Duke,

00:03:15.100 --> 00:03:17.100
the former head of the KKK,

00:03:17.100 --> 00:03:22.700
was quick to congratulate Laura Ingraham
and say that what he had heard her say

00:03:22.700 --> 00:03:26.460
on the TV was "the most important and
truthful monologue

00:03:26.460 --> 00:03:28.820
