00:03:51.220 --> 00:03:53.420
It's an invasion of drugs and criminals.

00:03:53.420 --> 00:03:57.660
And in some cases, you have killers coming
in and murderers coming in

00:03:57.660 --> 00:03:59.140
and we're not going to allow that to happen."

00:03:59.140 --> 00:04:02.300
It's galling to see that language also
come out

00:04:02.300 --> 00:04:04.060
