their rise on the world stage.

00:04:12.940 --> 00:04:19.700
Until we as people who live in ostensibly
liberal societies can stress

00:04:19.700 --> 00:04:23.260
that it's important to find solidarity
in our differences,

00:04:23.620 --> 00:04:26.100
bigotry of this kind is
only going to get stronger.

